com.exsoinn.util

Class EscapeUtil

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.exsoinn.util.EscapeUtil

  • public class EscapeUtil
extends Object
    Encapsulate logic to "escape" characters that create issues when trying to form JSON from strings that contain such characters. This class contains methods for both escaping and unescaping, escapeSpecialCharacters(String) and unescapeSpecialCharacters(String) respectively. Created by QuijadaJ on 8/15/2017.
